<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="border-spacing:0;border-collapse:separate">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="border-collapse:collapse;">
        <table cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:20px">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="border-collapse:collapse;padding-bottom:10px">
                <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0">
                  Hello $pi,
                  <br><br>
                  OpenSpecimen is a biospecimen information management system utilized by research laboratories at $hostingInstitute and you are listed as the Principal Investigator for the study listed below.
                  For compliance reasons, we would like you to verify the study coordinators listed are still authorized to access your study data.
                  <br><br>
                  <table>
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td> <b>Collection Protocol Short Title</b> </td>
                        <td> : $cpShortTitle </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td> <b>List of Coordinators</b> </td>
                        <td> : $coordinators </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                  <br><br>
                  If any of these study coordinators do not need access to the study data going forward, please email to our Help Desk at $helpdeskEmail, with user details so that our administrator can deactivate access.
                  <br><br>
                  If you have any questions related to this email, please contact us at $contactEmail.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td>
        #parse( $footer )
      </td>
    <tr>
  </tbody>
</table>